Set alignment of Widgets

Center vertically
Column(
  mainAxisAlignment: MainAxisAlignment.center,
  children: <Widget>[ ... ],
)
Center horizontally
Column(
  crossAxisAlignment: CrossAxisAlignment.center,
  children: <Widget>[ ... ],
)
But if the column is hugging its content then just wrap it in a Center widget

Center(
  child: Column(
    children: <Widget>[ ... ],
  ),
)
